FT  20 FEB 93 / Finance and the Family: Advice for investors - At a glance
The Consumers' Association has published a new edition of its its guide to
investment strategies and choices. It contains chapters on getting advice,
tax, investing for children, and pensions along with explanations of the
main investment products. 'Which? Way to Save and Invest,' Consumers'
Association and Hodder &amp; Stoughton, Pounds 12.99
